&lt;p&gt;As our Central Expansion Lead, you own how Gigs enters new markets, end to end, across every country we launch. You&#39;re not running a single market; you&#39;re the central operator who ensures new markets launch in parallel, on time, and to the same high standard.&lt;/p&gt;
